          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Can you lose all your money in the S&P 500?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "To lose all your money in an S&P 500 index fund, all 500 of America's largest companies (like Apple, Microsoft, and Amazon) would have to simultaneously go bankrupt. While temporary market crashes happen, a complete loss is practically impossible."
